-- Adidas Shifts from TV, Print to Online Advertising, Handelsblatt Reports
-- B y   E v a   v o n   S c h a p e r
-- 2010-11-26T06:44:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-26/adidas-shifts-to-online-advertising-handelsblatt-reports.html
Adidas AG  is shifting its
advertising spend from TV and print media to the internet,
 Handelsblatt  reported, citing Adidas board member  Erich Stamminger .  The company spent about 1.5 billion euros ($2 billion) on
advertising this year, the newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Serafino at   pserafino@bloomberg.net  